      <note type="warning" class="- topic/note ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">Swinging/wide loads and a reduced residual capacity can result in accidents. </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">Adapt the travel speed to the load, less than walking pace. </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">Secure swinging loads for example with lifting slings. </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">Reduce the residual capacity and have it certified by an expert. </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">Failure to follow the operation precautions may cause early damage to parts. </p>
      </note>
